
Slide and Glide - Privacy Policy
Effective Date: 3 March 2024

Introduction

This Privacy Policy is for Slide and Glide (the "Game"), a game developed by [Your Name/Studio Name] ("we", "us", or "our"). This Privacy Policy informs you that the Game does not collect any personal information from users.

Information We Do Not Collect

The Game does not collect any of the following information:

Device identifiers (like UDID or Advertising ID)
Location data (GPS)
Contact information (email address, phone number)
Gameplay data beyond what's stored locally on the device (scores, progress)
In-app purchases (the game is assumed to be free)
Transparency and Commitment

We are committed to user privacy and believe in a transparent approach. By design, the Game operates entirely on your device and does not transmit any data for us to collect.

Changes to this Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on the Game.

Contact Us

If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at slyzasocials@gmail.com.
